<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Beauty Tips by Chirag</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      margin: 0;
      background: #fff0f5;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      background: #ff69b4;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      margin: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px gray;
    }

    button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #ff69b4;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    footer {
      background: #333;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  💄 Beauty Tips Website 💄
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">
    <h2>✨ Glowing Skin Tip</h2>
    <p>Roz subah garam paani + nimbu peeyo. Skin naturally glow karegi.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🌿 Hair Care Tip</h2>
    <p>Hafte me 2 baar coconut oil se massage karo. Baal strong honge.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🧴 Face Care</h2>
    <p>Raat ko sone se pehle face wash zaroor karo. Pimples kam honge.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>🍎 Healthy Diet</h2>
    <p>Fruits aur pani zyada lo. Skin aur hair dono healthy rahenge.</p>
  </div>

  <button onclick="alert('Stay Beautiful 😍')">Click for Magic ✨</button>

</div>

<footer>
  Made by Chirag 🚀
</footer>

</body>
</html>
